@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Home Page";
}

<div class="jumbotron">
    <h1>tFX Tool</h1>
    <p class="lead">tFX tool is a free resource that aids individuals in Forex trading. It curates & gives real time feeds on sentiments / fundamental analysis, 
    signals from relevant & certified FX experts. It houses an equity table, calculator, standardized formula that can be used for buying & selling in the market.</p>
